01:00:21.330 --> 01:00:24.070
equals 0, which is
normally right here.

01:00:24.070 --> 01:00:25.980
So this thing actually
goes over to the right

01:00:25.980 --> 01:00:28.440
and we'll get positive
and negative values

01:00:28.440 --> 01:00:32.160
and it should lie along
