01:04:51.230 --> 01:04:55.250
And in Kempe's construction
he wants each of the things

01:04:55.250 --> 01:04:57.360
that we call the
parallelogram like this one,

01:04:57.360 --> 01:04:59.127
to stay on one, the
parallelogram track.

01:04:59.127 --> 01:05:00.710
And he wants the
